Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.16,0:27:31.26,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}將第一個約定的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.26,0:27:35.66,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}緊握到疼痛 絕不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.96,0:27:41.60,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}帶着任性的現在 前往不屬於任何人的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.60,0:27:44.30,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H181818&}從那裏開始吧
